- Go.

304
00:26:27.921 --> 00:26:30.174
Alpha. patient one en route.

305
00:26:45.856 --> 00:26:48.692
Alpha. patient two has just arrived.
On his way to intake.

306
00:26:49.276 --> 00:26:52.404
Thank you. Hatef.
We're ready at our positions.

307
