Don't go to Azizi. It's dangerous.

446
00:43:33.614 --> 00:43:35.449
My love. I've prepared everything. okay?

447
00:43:35.532 --> 00:43:37.910
Okay? I'm right by his stand.
We don't have a choice.

448
00:43:37.993 --> 00:43:41.163
Yes. we do. We do.
